  "texts": [
    "We train BioBERT on both datasets (i.e.",
    "GENIA and BC5CDR) for 20 epochs with learning rate of 3e-5.",
    "4 https://huggingface.co/dmis-lab/biobert-v1.1 KB Augmentation.",
    "Inspired from the training process of language models that learn reliable knowledge from the train set, we add entities from the train set to KB as reliable knowledge.",
    "It is a fair setting because the entities are not directly assigned as the answer because not only the exact span, but also other multiple spans are given as candidates, and LLM has to choose the answer among them."
  ],
